format: This data frame contains the following columns:

parameters.cens: The censoring indicator; 1 means right-censored data.
parameters.time: The failure or censoring time in hours.

description:
Description
The hirose data frame has 44 rows and 3 columns.
PET film is used in electrical insulation.  In this accelerated life test
the failure times for 44 samples in gas insulated transformers.  4 different
voltage levels were used.
title: Failure Time of PET Film
